      "title": "Pairs That Multiply",
      "content": "Factor pairs are two factors that multiply to the number. For 15, one pair is (3,5).",
      "visual_type": "none",
      "visual_data": {},
      "tts": "Factor pairs are two factors that multiply to the number. For 15, one pair is (3,5)."
